}}'''ESLint'''用於檢查[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]程式碼是否符合規則，由Nicholas C. Zakas在2013年建立。<ref>{{Cite web|title=First commit - eslint/eslint|url=https://github.com/eslint/eslint/commit/a658d7b0e7d915750f18d666823d54ef2129a9af|accessdate=2019-07-05|work=GitHub|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210629162207/https://github.com/eslint/eslint/commit/a658d7b0e7d915750f18d666823d54ef2129a9af}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Introducing ESLint|url=https://www.nczonline.net/blog/2013/07/16/introducing-eslint/|accessdate=2018-02-26|author=Zakas|date=16 July 2013|first=Nicholas C.|work=nczonline.net|language=en-US|quote=JSLint was the state of the art in JavaScript linting technology|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226092246/https://www.nczonline.net/blog/2013/07/16/introducing-eslint/}}</ref>ESLint中的規則是可更改的，並且可以自行定義和加載規則。ESLint想要解決關於{{tsl|en|Coding conventions|程式碼約定|程式碼品質}}和[[程式碼風格|程式碼風格]]的問題。ESLint支援[[ECMAScript|ECMAScript]]當前標準以及草案中用於未來標準的實驗語法。使用[[React|JSX]]或[[TypeScript|TypeScript]]的程式也可以透過外掛或轉譯器處理。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The future of TypeScript on ESLint|url=https://eslint.org/blog/2019/01/future-typescript-eslint|accessdate=2020-04-24|work=ESLint - Pluggable JavaScript linter|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413204615/https://eslint.org/blog/2019/01/future-typescript-eslint}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Accessibility auditing with eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y|url=https://web.dev/accessibility-auditing-react/|accessdate=2020-04-24|date=2019-04-29|work=web.dev|publisher=Google Developers|language=en|quote=The [ELint plugin] can help pinpoint [issues] in your JSX.|archive-date=2021-02-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210201112822/https://web.dev/accessibility-auditing-react/}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==
JSLint和[[JSHint|JSHint]]都缺乏為了程式碼品質和程式碼風格新增規則的能力。<ref name=":1" />在為JSHint做出貢獻之後，Zakas決定在2013年6月建立一個新的[[Lint|整理]]工具ESLint（最初稱為JSCheck，但在一個月後更名），其中所有規則都可更改，並且可以在[[運行時|運行時]]定義或加載其他規則。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://blog.rangle.io/understanding-the-real-advantages-of-using-eslint/|title=Understanding the Real Advantages of Using ESLint|date=2015-03-26|work=Rangle.io Blog|accessdate=2018-02-26|archive-date=2019-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209232042/https://blog.rangle.io/understanding-the-real-advantages-of-using-eslint/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Rename project to ESLint · eslint/eslint@4f4c351|url=https://github.com/eslint/eslint/commit/4f4c3519502645297bac6f6d9509d71980dc320e|accessdate=2020-06-26|date=4 July 2013|work=GitHub|language=en|archive-date=2021-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211223035955/https://github.com/eslint/eslint/commit/4f4c3519502645297bac6f6d9509d71980dc320e}}</ref>

2016年4月，ESLint項目加入了{{tsl|en|jQuery Foundation}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=ESLint Joins The jQuery Foundation|url=https://eslint.org/blog/2016/04/eslint-joins-the-jquery-foundation|accessdate=2019-07-05|author=Zakas|date=19 April 2016|first=Nicholas|work=eslint.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127101615/https://eslint.org/blog/2016/04/eslint-joins-the-jquery-foundation}}</ref>隨後，jQuery Foundation與Dojo Foundation合併，成为Linux Foundation其中的{{tsl|en|JS Foundation}}。<ref>{{Cite web|title=jQuery Foundation and Dojo Foundation to Merge|url=https://blog.jquery.com/2015/09/01/jquery-foundation-and-dojo-foundation-to-merge/|accessdate=2018-07-02|date=1 September 2015|work=Official jQuery Blog|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209185740/https://blog.jquery.com/2015/09/01/jquery-foundation-and-dojo-foundation-to-merge/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.prweb.com/releases/2015/08/prweb12931885.htm|title=jQuery Foundation and Dojo Foundation to Merge|date=1 July 2015|work=PRWeb|accessdate=2018-07-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112706/http://www.prweb.com/releases/2015/08/prweb12931885.htm}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.sitepen.com/blog/2016/10/17/announcing-the-js-foundation/|title=Announcing the JS Foundation!|date=2016-10-17|work=SitePen|accessdate=2018-07-02|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925132900/https://www.sitepen.com/blog/2016/10/17/announcing-the-js-foundation/}}</ref>

2017年10月，ESLint從JS Foundation的mentorship program畢業。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://js.foundation/announcements/2017/10/05/eslint-graduates-from-js-foundation-mentorship-program|title=ESLint Graduates from JS Foundation Mentorship Program|date=2017-10-05|work=JS Foundation Blog|accessdate=2019-07-05|language=en-US|archive-date=2019-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705195320/https://js.foundation/announcements/2017/10/05/eslint-graduates-from-js-foundation-mentorship-program}}</ref>

2019年3月，JS Foundation和Node.js Foundation合併之後成為OpenJS Foundation的一部份。<ref name="verge-openjsfoundation">{{Cite news|url=https://venturebeat.com/2019/03/12/node-js-and-js-foundations-are-merging-to-form-openjs/|title=Node.js and JS foundations are merging to form OpenJS|author=Singh|first=Manish|date=2019-03-12|work=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|accessdate=2019-03-21|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211012644/https://venturebeat.com/2019/03/12/node-js-and-js-foundations-are-merging-to-form-openjs/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://js.foundation/announcements/2018/10/04/the-node-js-foundation-and-js-foundation-announce-an-intent-to-merge-a-message-from-the-boards-and-a-faq-around-the-announcement|title=The Node.js Foundation and JS Foundation Announce an Intent to Merge|date=2018-10-04|work=JS Foundation Blog|accessdate=2019-07-05|language=en-US|quote=How will this impact the technical direction of … ESLint This will not change the technical independence for projects like ESLint.|archive-date=2019-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190705195321/https://js.foundation/announcements/2018/10/04/the-node-js-foundation-and-js-foundation-announce-an-intent-to-merge-a-message-from-the-boards-and-a-faq-around-the-announcement}}</ref>

== 支援 ==
自2015年起，[[JetBrains|JetBrains]]於其WebStorm程式碼編輯器中內建支援ESLint，可對當前開啟的文件運行ESLint，並在編輯器中有問題的程式碼附近顯示警告。<ref>{{Cite web|title=WebStorm Linting, refactoring and compiling|url=https://blog.jetbrains.com/webstorm/2015/12/working-with-reactjs-in-webstorm-linting-refactoring-and-compiling/|accessdate=2019-07-05|date=30 December 2015|work=WebStorm Blog|publisher=[[JetBrains|JetBrains]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225061433/https://blog.jetbrains.com/webstorm/2015/12/working-with-reactjs-in-webstorm-linting-refactoring-and-compiling/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Using JavaScript Standard Style|url=https://blog.jetbrains.com/webstorm/2017/04/using-javascript-standard-style/|accessdate=2019-07-05|date=7 April 2017|work=WebStorm Blog|publisher=[[JetBrains|JetBrains]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128130915/https://blog.jetbrains.com/webstorm/2017/04/using-javascript-standard-style/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=ESLint - WebStorm Manual|url=https://www.jetbrains.com/help/webstorm/eslint.html|accessdate=2019-07-05|publisher=[[JetBrains|JetBrains]]|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111195953/https://www.jetbrains.com/help/webstorm/eslint.html}}</ref>

2016年，[[Vue.js|Vue.js]]項目提供了一個ESLint外掛來自動驗證Vue.js模板和其他功能的使用。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Writing Vue.js Applications in TypeScript|url=https://blog.kloud.com.au/2017/02/24/writing-vuejs-apps-in-typescript-on-aspnet-core/|accessdate=2019-07-05|publisher=[[Telstra|Telstra]] Kloud|archive-date=2020-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401093834/https://blog.kloud.com.au/2017/02/24/writing-vuejs-apps-in-typescript-on-aspnet-core/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Lesson: Automatic Linting with ESLint - The Vue.js Master Class|url=https://vueschool.io/the-vuejs-master-class|accessdate=2019-07-05|work=Vue School|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210204142847/https://vueschool.io/the-vuejs-master-class/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Introduction {{!}} eslint-plugin-vue|url=https://eslint.vuejs.org/|accessdate=2019-07-05|work=eslint.vuejs.org|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225052334/https://eslint.vuejs.org/}}</ref>從2018年開始，[[精靈_(軟體)|Vue CLI]]建立新Vue.js項目時也會建議使用該外掛。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Vue Handbook: a thorough introduction to Vue.js|url=https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/the-vue-handbook-a-thorough-introduction-to-vue-js-1e86835d8446/|accessdate=2019-07-05|date=2018-07-05|work=Developer News|language=en|quote=Use the interactive CLI to create a new Vue project [..] By default, there is [..] ESLint integration|archive-date=2021-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210121171256/https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/the-vue-handbook-a-thorough-introduction-to-vue-js-1e86835d8446/}}</ref>

在2018年10月，[[React|React]]（由[[Facebook|Facebook]]開發）發布了一個官方的ESLint外掛來幫助執行其編程規則。<ref>{{Cite web|title=ESLint Plugin – Rules of Hooks – React Manual|url=https://reactjs.org/docs/hooks-rules.html|accessdate=2019-07-05|work=reactjs.org|language=en|archive-date=2021-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606174151/https://reactjs.org/docs/hooks-rules.html}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Implement the Hooks proposal · facebook/react|url=https://github.com/facebook/react/pull/13968|accessdate=2019-07-05|author=Markbåge|date=25 October 2018|first=Sebastian|work=GitHub|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112035446/https://github.com/facebook/react/pull/13968}}</ref>

截至2021年，ESLint是最常用的JavaScript linter，每周被下載超過14,000,000次。<ref>{{Cite web|title=jslint vs jshint vs eslint vs tslint vs @typescript eslint/eslint plugin|url=https://www.npmtrends.com/jslint-vs-jshint-vs-eslint-vs-tslint-vs-@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin|accessdate=2021-01-26|work=www.npmtrends.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202175616/https://www.npmtrends.com/jslint-vs-jshint-vs-eslint-vs-tslint-vs-@typescript-eslint/eslint-plugin}}</ref>

